---
import 'animate.css'
---
<div class="container font-sans">
    <h2 class="container text-5xl heading2 font-sans text-center">Trayectoria</h2>
    <ol class="relative border-l border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">   
        <li class="mb-10 ml-4 animate__pulse">
            <time class="mb-1 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500">May 2022 - Presente</time>
            <div class="current absolute w-3 h-3 rounded-full mt-1.5 -left-1.5 border"></div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Balloon Group, <span class="text-sm font-normal">Argentina</span></h3>
            <p class="mb-4 text-base font-normal text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Líder técnico para la celula vtex, desarrollando soluciones web con react, graphql, node, entre otras tecnologías en proyectos para
                circlek, animarama, .</p>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/balloon-group/mycompany/" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 focus:z-10 focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-gray-200 focus:text-blue-700 dark:focus:ring-gray-700">
                <img class="w-8 m-4 icons-testimonials cursor-pointer" src="/icons/linkedin.png" />
                <p class="dark:text-gray-400 text-gray-500 cursor-pointer">linkedin</p>
            </a>
        </li>               
        <li class="mb-10 ml-4">
            <time class="mb-1 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500">Jun 2021 - May 2022</time>
            <div class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-gray-200 rounded-full mt-1.5 -left-1.5 border border-white dark:border-gray-900 dark:bg-gray-700"></div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">ITGlobers, <span class="text-sm font-normal">Colombia</span></h3>
            <p class="mb-4 text-base font-normal text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Desarrollador frontend para grandes proyectos como tiendas jumbo, metro, easy, jefferspet y shade of lights.</p>
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/itglobers/" class="inline-flex items-center px-4 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 focus:z-10 focus:ring-4 focus:outline-none focus:ring-gray-200 focus:text-blue-700 dark:focus:ring-gray-700">
                <img class="w-8 m-4 icons-testimonials cursor-pointer" src="/icons/linkedin.png" />
                <p class="dark:text-gray-400 text-gray-500 cursor-pointer">linkedin</p>
            </a>
        </li>
        <li class="mb-10 ml-4">
            <time class="mb-1 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500">Feb 2019 - Jul 2020</time>
            <div class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-gray-200 rounded-full mt-1.5 -left-1.5 border border-white dark:border-gray-900 dark:bg-gray-700"></div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Ingenyo S.A.S, <span class="text-sm font-normal">Colombia</span></h3>
            <p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Desarrollo de página web, Administrador de sistemas de información.</p>
        </li>
        <li class="ml-4 mb-20">
            <time class="mb-1 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500">Nov 2018 - Dic 2019</time>
            <div class="absolute w-3 h-3 bg-gray-200 rounded-full mt-1.5 -left-1.5 border border-white dark:border-gray-900 dark:bg-gray-700"></div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Fundación Fátima, <span class="text-sm font-normal">Colombia</span></h3>
            <p class="text-base font-normal text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Desarrollo de página web, Administrador de sistemas de información.</p>
        </li>
    </ol>
</div>

<style>
    .current{
        background-color: var(--action-color);
        border-color: var(--action-color);
    }

    .pulse:hover{
        -webkit-animation: bounce 2s;
        animation: bounce 2s;  
    }
    .heading2{
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-weight: 400;
  }
</style>
